Second edition of annual BOHEMA longsword event - from fencers to fencers! At least 10 fights guaranteed.

3 Tiers of participation:
- women+ up to 48 fencers
- basic(core) up to 144 fencers
- advance(hardcore) up to 48 fencers

Advanced criteria: win medals in Basic or Open Longsword with 40+ participants for last 3 years. Or contact us if you don't have it, but still want to advance.

Basic: Don't have medals in Basic or Open Longsword with 40+ participants for last 3 years.

- fight me zone
- pool party
- full streaming
- refreshments
- facebook drama
- epic prizes
- equipment back ups

But, there is more!

3000 EUR cash prize for top 4 people in advanced

2 video-reviews per fencers since eliminations for all tier

Easton Longswords as provided weapons. (1700 grams, 18 kg flex)

Dates: September 27-28.

Participation: 90 EUR.

Seals of Purity: Yes!
